  "title": "Sales & Marketing Specialist (FUN ENVIRONMENT)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Looking for more than a desk job?</strong></em></p><p><br />If you’re seeking a role that’s dynamic, people-focused, and growth-oriented, we may be the right fit.</p><p></p><p><em>Key responsibilities:</em></p><p>• Represent brands at events, pop-ups, and roadshows</p><p>• Engage with customers through face-to-face interactions</p><p>• Promote products and campaigns in a professional setting</p><p>• Develop sales, communication, and confidence skills</p><p>• Earn based on performance, with clear earning potential</p><p>• Participate in travel opportunities for events and team activities</p><p><br /></p><p><em>This role is ideal for candidates who:</em></p><p>• Are energetic, motivated, and professional</p><p>• Enjoy working with people and building rapport</p><p>• Are looking to move beyond traditional 9–5 roles</p><p>• Want structured development and career progression</p><p><br /></p><p><em>What we offer:</em></p><p>• Supportive team environment</p><p>• Ongoing training and mentorship</p><p>• Performance-based compensation</p><p>• Clear advancement opportunities</p><p><br /></p><p>No prior experience is required — full training is provided.</p><p><br /></p><p>👉 Apply now to begin a role where your growth and performance are rewarded.</p>",
